In [27]:
#make the values which are 0 as Unansweredmake the values which are in 1-20 range as 'Twenty',make the values which are in 21-40 range as 'Forty',make the values which are in 41-60 range as 'Sixty', make the values which are in 61-80 range as 'Eighty'
df.loc[(df['Answers'] >=1) & (df['Answers'] <= 20), 'Ans'] = 'Twenty'
df.loc[(df['Answers']==0),'Ans'] = 'Unanswered'
df.loc[(df['Answers'] >=21) & (df['Answers'] <= 40), 'Ans'] = 'Forty'
df.loc[(df['Answers'] >=41) & (df['Answers'] <= 60), 'Ans'] = 'Sixty'
df.loc[(df['Answers'] >=61) & (df['Answers'] <= 80), 'Ans'] = 'Eighty'
df
